}
</code></pre>
<p>So far, I can make an element filling the context with mouse data and some methods to update them. I can't find a way to &quot;call&quot; my children when this data is updated, without reconstructing them.</p>
<pre><code>#[derive(Clone, Copy, Debug)]
pub struct DragState {
    drag_origin: Signal&lt;ElementPoint&gt;,
